# Project-local generated state and large research assets.
#
# The GitHub repository tracks source code, protocol configs, paper-facing
# metadata, and dataset/download documentation. It intentionally does not track
# raw datasets, generated experiment outputs, model weights, caches, virtual
# environments, or temporary scratch files.

# Editors / OS
.vscode/
.idea/
.DS_Store

